# APB Slave – RTL Design & UVM Verification Environment

## Overview

This project implements a **fully protocol-compliant APB (AMBA Peripheral Bus) Slave** in
SystemVerilog and verifies it with a complete **UVM-based testbench** covering:

- Correct APB setup/enable two-phase handshake
- Address decoding (8 × 32-bit word-aligned registers)
- Byte-strobe (PSTRB) write granularity
- Configurable wait-state insertion via PREADY
- PSLVERR signalling for invalid accesses

