```
Clock  : ___/‾‾‾\___/‾‾‾\___/‾‾‾\___/‾‾‾\___
         |       |       |       |       |
PSEL   : ________/‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾\_____
PENABLE: ______________/‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾‾\_______
PREADY : ________________/‾‾‾‾‾‾‾\___________ ← DUT de-asserts during wait states
         IDLE   SETUP    ENABLE(ws) ENABLE  IDLE
