## DUT Register Map

| Offset | Register | Reset Value |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| 0x00   | REG0     | 0x0000_0000 |
| 0x04   | REG1     | 0x0000_0000 |
| 0x08   | REG2     | 0x0000_0000 |
| 0x0C   | REG3     | 0x0000_0000 |
| 0x10   | REG4     | 0x0000_0000 |
| 0x14   | REG5     | 0x0000_0000 |
| 0x18   | REG6     | 0x0000_0000 |
| 0x1C   | REG7     | 0x0000_0000 |

Addresses ≥ 0x20 or non-word-aligned → **PSLVERR = 1**

