## Coverage

The `apb_coverage` subscriber samples:

- Transfer direction (`READ` / `WRITE`)
- All 8 register addresses + invalid bins
- All useful byte-strobe patterns
- PSLVERR assertion
- Cross coverage: direction × address, direction × error